The paper deals with the security and scalability issues in IoT data sharing, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of blockchain technology, which is related to databases (cs.DB) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the paper proposes the use of smart contracts, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
